Eidolon::Driver::User::Basic, version 0.02
==========================================

The Eidolon::Driver::User::Basic is a user driver for Eidolon, that
provides simple session-based authorization.

INSTALLATION

To install the driver type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

To use this driver you must have the following packages installed:

    Eidolon

